Licensing
=========

This repository contains code and assets under multiple licences.

The applicable licence is determined by the file-level notice where one is
present.

- EEL Accounts application-specific files are licensed under the GNU Affero
  General Public License version 3.0 (AGPLv3).
- eelKit framework files are licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License.
- Bundled font files under web_root/fonts are licensed under the SIL Open Font
  License version 1.1 (OFL-1.1).
- Arelle integration files under third_party/arelle document and wrap the
  separately distributed Arelle validator, which is Apache-2.0 licensed.

If a file does not contain an explicit licence notice, treat the surrounding
directory, file purpose, and project history as the guide:

- EEL Accounts application files are AGPLv3.
- eelKit framework files are BSD 3-Clause.
- Font assets remain under their upstream font licences.
- Third-party validator runtimes, caches, taxonomies, and logs under
  third_party/arelle are governed by their upstream licences and local install
  terms.

Full licence texts are included in:

- LICENSES/AGPL-3.0.txt
- LICENSES/BSD-3-Clause.txt
- LICENSES/OFL-1.1.txt

The font directories also retain their upstream licence files:

- web_root/fonts/LICENSE
- web_root/fonts/Inter/OFL.txt
- web_root/fonts/Roboto/OFL.txt
